pageProduct.name: Swisse Ultiboost Liver Detox 60 Tablets
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Suitable For: Vegetarians

Size: 60 Pack

Warnings

Do not use if pregnant or likely to become pregnant. If symptoms persist, consult your healthcare practitioner. Do not use if cap seal is broken.

Ingredients

Global Artichoke (Cynara scolymus extract 20mg) equiv. fresh leaf 1g. Standardised extracts equivalent to dry: Milk Thistle (Silybum marianum extract 35.71mg) equiv. dry fruit (standardised to contain flavanolignans calculated as silybin 28.6mg) 2.5g; Turmeric (Curcuma longa extract 75mg) equiv. dry rhizome (standardised to contain curcuminoids 48.75mg) 1.5g. Contains soya beans.

Contains: Contains soya beans.

Allergen Contains: Milk| Soybean

Allergen Free From: Gluten| Lactose

Directions

Adult Dosage:
Two tablets daily, during or immediately after a meal, or as directed by a healthcare professional.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 30°C.

RECYCLABLE INFORMATION

Swisse is a carbon neutral company. Please recycle.

Recyclable Packaging?: Yes
